{"tid":1064094,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"<足球歷史> 請問摩連奴喺皇馬做咗啲咩咁克人憎?","createTime":"2019-03-16T09:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T09:45:16.000Z","uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cddbacdc038db0449ed9b2c907a48c82bf9df8f0","tid":1064094,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:40:40.000Z","msg":"最近睇緊施丹回歸既新聞<br />\n好多新聞話佩雷斯係想請返摩連奴多過施丹<br />\n但係更衣室大佬唔贊成所以作罷<br />\n<br />\n報紙話摩連奴破壞咗好多野<br />\n究竟摩佬破壞咗啲乜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我靜係知卡斯拿斯間諜單野, 咁雪藏佢又製造咗啲咩破壞?<br />\n唔通依家搵25圖做龍, 拿華斯做後備又冇破壞咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真心想知當年摩佬係皇馬做咗啲咩傷天害理既野?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab64c06fe504911ca2801af28af95b6be29b312","tid":1064094,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:43:57.000Z","msg":"我諗摩佬應該同雲鳩耳一樣都係高壓鐵腕個類管治手法<br />\n大牌既球員唔會頂得順"},{"pid":"3e20696b2e7ad80d6ea97747ff064317ee26ddf8","tid":1064094,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"同喺曼聯一樣<br />\n<br />\n搞更衣室"},{"pid":"478a45525e208902153d884af1b27a535da78c05","tid":1064094,"uid":137248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:45:16.000Z","msg":"搞尻卡斯拿斯同拉莫斯西班牙幫"}]}